		{
			"id":"cfaf726d96a9ae10",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"[CPP Core  Guidelines](https://cpp-core-guidelines-docs.vercel.app/introduction)\n[Core Guide](https://isocpp.github.io/CppCoreGuidelines/CppCoreGuidelines#main)\n[400 вопросов С++](https://github.com/Jollu8/C-INTERVIEW-QUESTIONS/blob/main/questions-400/junior.md)\n[Паттерны y2k](https://y2kot.gitbook.io/untitled/patterns/creationals-patterns/abstract-factory/realizacii-na-s++)\n[Алгоритмы Диапазонов](https://y2kot.gitbook.io/untitled/patterns/creationals-patterns/abstract-factory/realizacii-na-s++)\n[Cmake туториал](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/latest/guide/tutorial/index.html)\n[Сайт умного мужика на анг, там тоже корунтины были](https://vishalchovatiya.com/posts\n[Путеводитель по неопр поведению](https://github.com/Nekrolm/ubbook)\n\n---\nLern cpp и его брат аналог:\n\nhttps://ravesli.com/uroki-cpp/\nhttps://www.learncpp.com/\n",
			"styleAttributes":{
				"textAlign":null,
				"border":null
			},
			"x":-3640,
			"y":860,
			"width":600,
